briefdescription.para: Failed to load any of the TO configuration tables - loading a backup tables - (per-channel event).

xrefdescription.para: Loaded built-in emergency backup config table! - channel %u

detaileddescription.para:
Type: INFORMATION
Cause:
This event message (per-channel event) is issued when TO has loaded the built-in emergency backup configuration table because cFE TBL was not able to provide a table.

briefdescription.para: TO Classifier failed to process a telemetry message - message too long - (per-channel event).

xrefdescription.para: Message too long (size = %lu > max = %d) for msgId = (0x%04X) on channel (%u)

detaileddescription.para:
Type: ERROR
Cause:
This event message (per-channel event) is issued when the CFS TO Task attempts to process a telemetry message length that is larger than TO_MAX_MSG_LENGTH.

briefdescription.para: Classifier failed to retrieve a message flow - Message ID in the table - (per-channel event).

xrefdescription.para: Classifier Recvd invalid msgId (0x%04X) or message flow was removed on channel (%u)

detaileddescription.para:
Type: ERROR
Cause:
This event message (per-channel event) is issued when the CFS TO Task attempts to retrieve a message flow and the Message ID is not in the table.

briefdescription.para: Failed loading a TO backup configuration table - (per-channel event).

xrefdescription.para: Failed to load built-in emergency backup config table! - channel %u

detaileddescription.para:
Type: ERROR
Cause:
This event message (per-channel event) is issued when CFE_TBL_Load failed to load the built-in emergency backup configuration table.

briefdescription.para: This is a count of all the app events and should not be used.
